    "7400317": {
        "Desc": "Continue onward",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "\"Someone\" wants this tale of adventure to never end."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Eh? What are you on about, {NICKNAME}?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh. You know what? Paimon thought that she hadn't fully woken up yet... But haven't these things happened before?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But the future of a story that constantly repeats will never come."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But we must keep moving forward."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "Yes..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Princess Lyris waits at the end of this path."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ooh, Paimon knows! The last time we were here, you said \"On the other hand, we'll be able to leave as long as we find the end of the road,\" didn't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Then there must be a way!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
