    "7400320": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Ann",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So... Why did we meet Narcissus in here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "According to what we said before, the tower lost its \"time\" and thus stagnated. As such, no one could open it or enter it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But this space is not within the tower."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We teleported to a different place from the tower."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, that's right! Paimon forgot that that happened... But if that's the case..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "But how... No, that can't be true! The Princess should be in the tower. I mean, that was the adventure team's only hope in this dark world..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "If she isn't... Our adventures... their meaning... Al, Petit Chou, and the others..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ann..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But we did take out the biggest threat to the kingdom, didn't we? That's a good thing, right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "...Yes, you're right, Paimon. Thank you. Thank you both."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Anyway, the story's not over."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yup! Look over there. There's a place we haven't been to before. Maybe we'll find more clues there, huh?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
