    "7400327": {
        "Desc": "Look for clues",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm? There's a book here too..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "A picture book, huh? It suits you, Paimon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmph! Well, that's because of Paimon's unique sensibility, you know? Picture books just speak to her better!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "This book... This book gives me a strange feeling."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let Paimon see..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"A long, long time ago, in a place far, far away, there was once a beautiful and kind Princess named Lyris... and yup, she's our main character!\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "\"'I don't want this name. That's not what you said before.'\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Do you wanna read it too, Ann? In that case, Paimon's gonna continue. Ahem!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Oh, come on, it's just a story, there's no need to be so fussy. Anyway, a protagonist needs an antagonist... an evil one, at that!\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"And our evil antagonist... Well, that's the dragon Narcissus. So evil is he that the peace-loving people tremble at the sound of his name — not that he cares about their feelings, though.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"He sowed destruction across the land with the searing flames he spewed from his mouth. His great wings turned cities to dust and his burning breath reduced nations to ash.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"At last, only the Princess's realm remained safe.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"But because the Princess worked tirelessly to defend her realm, Narcissus's plot to destroy everything could not succeed.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ann",
                    "T": "\"'So, in Narcissus's story, I'm the evil villain?'\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#This is kinda weird. This started like a story book, but it also feels like it isn't... {NICKNAME}, you've got the bigger brain here. You have a look too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Read carefully...)"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
